{"tid":2104104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[初選]有好多人成日問我：喂 Brian⋯⋯你究竟點投票㗎","createTime":"2020-07-11T16:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T06:40:59.000Z","uid":279136,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"79d868d6f15e8a3ae755a4c076434168261aac2d","tid":2104104,"uid":279136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:34:22.000Z","msg":"我尋日 搵左屋企附近個投票站 用咗幾分鐘就投完初選<br />\n好多人聽到可能會話 喂 brian 邊有可能呀？ 就係有可能！<br />\n拿, 你就咁聽我講幾句可能唔會信<br />\n<br />\n聽日9點至9點港九新界都有投票站，唔洗錢嘅，好多香港人都嚟架<br />\n聽完都係覺得我信唔過嘅，無所謂，當出嚟望一望，幫下啲長輩完成投票流程<br />\n但我有信心你聽完會了解到個投票方法，以你做香港人嘅智慧你會明<br />\n<br />\n我有個idea 係度，我試過係work 嘅，<br />\n你見唔見有得網上預先投票，再拎齊所有文件去排隊，個投票數字就會蹦蹦聲咁上<br />\n作為朋友我想分享比你知, 我相信你可以搞得仲快過我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd6570d6eff922f8b0fa5b7e1c80b6528ae3683","tid":2104104,"uid":279136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"初選教學 [附逐頁截圖]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2103342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2103342</a>"},{"pid":"480a3e214fd4c7f8733d48e455952cd39bc16290","tid":2104104,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27bac72e3a328d551ffd5ce3df7fb9ddcc26380b","tid":2104104,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"我排都唔使排，行到去即scan+對資料，半分鐘都無就走得。你太耐了要幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /